@@ -0,0 +1,32 @@
+import { FlatList, StyleSheet } from "react-native";
+import colors from '../../color'
+
+const styles = StyleSheet.create({
+
+  container: {
+    flex: 1,
+  },
+  listContent: {
+    paddingBottom: 16,
+  },
+  emptyContainer: {
+    flex: 1,
+    justifyContent: 'center',
+    alignItems: 'center',
+    marginTop: 20,
+  },
+  emptyImage: {
+    width: 150,
+    height: 150,
+    marginBottom: 10,
+  },
+  emptyText: {
+    fontSize: 18,
+    textAlign: 'center',
+    color: '#555',
+
+
+
+});
+
+export default styles;
